Interface OnMixpanelUpdatesReceivedListener


  • public interface OnMixpanelUpdatesReceivedListener
    For use with MixpanelAPI.People.addOnMixpanelUpdatesReceivedListener(OnMixpanelUpdatesReceivedListener)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onMixpanelUpdatesReceived()
      Called when the Mixpanel library has updates, for example, Surveys or Notifications.

    • Method Detail

      • onMixpanelUpdatesReceived

        void onMixpanelUpdatesReceived()
        Called when the Mixpanel library has updates, for example, Surveys or Notifications. This method will not be called once per update, but rather any time a batch of updates becomes available. The related updates can be checked with MixpanelAPI.People.getSurveyIfAvailable() or MixpanelAPI.People.getNotificationIfAvailable()
